# Contributing to Schule-als-Staat

Thank you for your interest in contributing to our project!

## How to Contribute

1. **Fork the repository and create a new branch**: Make a fork of the main repository, create a new branch for your feature or bug fix.

2. **Make your changes**: Implement your feature or fix a bug in your branch. Make sure to commit your changes in logical chunks.

3. **Test your changes**: Ensure that your changes do not break any existing functionality.

4. **Submit a Pull Request**: Once you're satisfied with your changes, push your branch to your forked repository on GitHub. Then, open a new pull request from your forked repository to the main repository.

## Code Style

Please follow the existing coding style to keep the code readable and consistent.

## Questions

If you have any questions, feel free to open an issue and we'll get back to you as soon as possible.

Thank you for your contributions!
